column1: Do you want to be in society?
column2: Do you make an attempt to socialise?
column3: Do you consume things to alter your perspective? (Alcohol and stuff)
column5: Do you try to improve yourself?
column6: Would you compromise with a friend?
column7: If you and another person were both thirsty and you only had enough water for one person; would you share with the other person?
column8: If a colleague invited you to do something with them; how would you answer? (Date; hang-out; party; etc.)
column9: Are you anxious of social interaction?
column10: Do you think you fit in with other people?
column11: Do you shower more than twice a week?
column12: Do you take care of your appearance? (shaving; hair styling; make up; fashion; etc.)
column13: Do you talk back in equal volume to someone that is talking to you? (Talking as much as they are to you and amplitude of voice)
column15: Does it seem unrealistic to imagine yourself with another person in an intimate context? (Girlfriend; best friends; etc)
column16: Do you have long term goals?
column17: Would you rather work in food service; or be unemployed?
column18: You've lived a life with many moments where you regret doing nothing.
column19: Is it reasonable to think that the majority of people are dumb?
column21: Are you currently celibate? (No sex for a while)
column22: Do you live your life by your own volition?
column23: Can you look people in the eyes without discomfort?
column24: Has anyone ever described you as awkward; autistic; weird; etc.?
column25: Do you currently have a romantic partner? (Unrequited(crushes); non-exclusive and/or non-monogamous relationships DO NOT count)
column26: Do you currently have a medium for socialization? (Social media; work; etc.)
column27: Do you talk to people on a regular basis? (Internet stuff doesn't count)
column28: Do you have unconventional interests? (Anime; collecting specific items; weird fetishes; etc.)
column29: Are you currently in education; training or employment?
column31: Is your family proud of you?
column32: Do people usually like being around you?
column39: How many friends and colleagues do you currently have?
column41: Which climate do you live in?
